 strapped to a table with a leather shock helmet</em><span>) that makes it =
unwanted by some patients. Ketamine, on the other hand, does not come with =
the same side effects, but does come with a stigma of its own &#8212; that =
it&#8217;s a horse-tranquilizing party-drug. </span></p><p style=3D"color: =
#404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Overall, =
