argin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Holy shit&#8230;AI is as dangerous as =
pandemics and nuclear war.</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p s=
tyle=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-heigh=
t: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">This is just AI i=
ndustry leaders pulling up the ladder by all-but begging for regulation.</p=
></li></ol><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; =
margin: 0 0 20px 0;">I think both are partially true. Yes, the worst-case A=
